{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775878640192,"sessionID":"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi","part":{"id":"prt_d7a9b8c63001RoWCXqvLmSYy2Y","messageID":"msg_d7a9b73890010XG5qi4Y1czrQm","sessionID":"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_21690f1ffbd940a3b7ce80fd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Helm Chart 模板与 Values 配置，提供标准的 Kubernetes 部署能力。该 Helm Chart 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的核心部署载体，支撑 Workload Manager、Router、以及可选的 Volcano Agent Scheduler 的安装与管理。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **标准化部署流程** - 通过 Helm Chart 统一控制平面组件的部署配置，支持一键安装/升级\n2. **配置灵活性** - 通过 values.yaml 提供完整的配置项，支持镜像、资源、副本数等自定义\n3. **CRD 生命周期管理** - 将 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 纳入 Chart 管理，随 Chart 安装\n4. **Redis 连接配置** - 支持 Redis 地址和认证的灵活配置，满足 Workload Manager 和 Router 运行时需求\n5. **可选组件支持** - 支持 Router RBAC、Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件的按需启用\n6. **多环境兼容** - 通过 values 覆盖支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化配置\n\n本实现基于 deployment/spec.md 和 deployment/design.md 的规范，遵循 Helm 3 最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** manifests  \n**Language:** YAML  \n**Size:** L\n\n本 AR 包含：\n\n- **包含内容：**\n  - Chart.yaml 实现（apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0）\n  - values.yaml 完整配置树（Redis、Router、WorkloadManager、Volcano Scheduler）\n  - Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 模板\n  - Router Deployment 和 Service 模板\n  - Workload Manager RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding）\n  - Router 可选 RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、Role、RoleBinding）\n  - Volcano Agent Scheduler 可选资源（ServiceAccount、ConfigMap、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding、Service、Deployment）\n  - CRD 文件（agentruntimes、codeinterpreters）\n  - .helmignore 文件\n  - 单元测试（values 验证、模板渲染测试）\n  - 安装文档和使用示例\n\n- **不包含内容：**\n  - Docker 镜像构建（由 docker/Dockerfile 单独管理）\n  - Redis 集群部署（作为外部依赖）\n  - 应用层代码修改\n  - 客户端 SDK 或 CLI 工具\n\n## Current State Analysis\n\n### 现有 manifests 结构\n\n根据 `manifests/charts/base/` 目录：\n- `crds/agentruntime.yaml` 已存在，包含 AgentRuntime CRD 定义\n- 缺少 CodeInterpreter CRD\n- 缺少 Chart.yaml、values.yaml 和 templates/\n\n### 参考设计规范\n\n根据 `deployment/design.md` 和 `deployment/spec.md`：\n\n**Chart.yaml 要求：**\n- apiVersion: v1\n- name: agentcube\n- version: 0.1.0\n- appVersion: 1.0.0\n\n**values.yaml 关键配置树：**\n- redis.addr / redis.password（必需配置）\n- router.replicas/image/service/resources/config/extraEnv/serviceAccountName/rbac\n- workloadmanager.replicas/image/service/resources/extraEnv\n- volcano.scheduler.enabled 及相关配置\n\n**模板文件要求：**\n- `templates/workloadmanager.yaml`: Deployment + Service\n- `templates/agentcube-router.yaml`: Deployment + Service\n- `templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`: ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n- `templates/rbac-router.yaml`: 可选的 Router RBAC\n- `templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`: 可选的 Volcano Scheduler\n\n**CRD 要求：**\n- `crds/agentruntimes`: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n- `crds/codeinterpreters`: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n\n### 差距分析\n\n1. **Chart 结构不完整** - 仅有 CRD，缺少 Chart.yaml、values.yaml 和 templates\n2. **CRD 不完整** - 缺少 CodeInterpreter CRD\n3. **缺少环境配置支持** - 无 values 覆盖机制，无法支持多环境部署\n4. **缺少 RBAC 定义** - Workload Manager 和 Router 的 RBAC 资源未定义\n5. **缺少可选组件支持** - Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件无法按需启用\n\n### deployment/spec.md 关键要求\n\n1. **Redis 配置** - `redis.addr` 和 `redis.password` 必须通过 values 配置，注入到 Pod 环境变量\n2. **Workload Manager 形状** - Deployment + Service，支持 replicas、image、resources、health probes\n3. **Router 形状** - Deployment + Service，支持 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 动态构建\n4. **RBAC 权限** - Workload Manager 需要 ClusterRole 访问 CRD、Pods、Secrets 等\n5. **可选 Router RBAC** - `router.rbac.create` 控制是否创建 namespace-scoped RBAC\n6. **可选 Volcano Scheduler** - `volcano.scheduler.enabled` 控制是否部署\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### 1. Chart.yaml\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml\napiVersion: v1\nname: agentcube\ndescription: A Helm chart for AgentCube\nversion: 0.1.0\nappVersion: \"1.0.0\"\nkeywords:\n  - agent\n  - sandbox\n  - kubernetes\n  - volcano\nhome: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\nsources:\n  - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\nmaintainers:\n  - name: Volcano Authors\n    email: volcano-sh@googlegroups.com\n```\n\n### 2. values.yaml\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/values.yaml\n# Default values for AgentCube.\n\n# Image pull secrets for all components\nimagePullSecrets: []\n\n# Override chart names\nnameOverride: \"\"\nfullnameOverride: \"\"\n\n# Redis configuration (required)\n# Redis address and password for Workload Manager and Router connectivity\nredis:\n  addr: \"\"          # e.g., \"redis.redis-system.svc.cluster.local:6379\"\n  password: \"\"      # Empty if Redis has no authentication\n\n# Router configuration\nrouter:\n  replicas: 1\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: \"latest\"\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n    targetPort: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  # Additional container configuration\n  config: {}\n  extraEnv: []\n  serviceAccountName: \"\"  # Empty means auto-generated or default\n  rbac:\n    create: false  # Enable namespace-scoped RBAC for Router\n\n# Workload Manager configuration\nworkloadmanager:\n  replicas: 1\n  image:\n    repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n    pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    tag: \"latest\"\n  service:\n    type: ClusterIP\n    port: 8080\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    requests:\n      cpu: 100m\n      memory: 128Mi\n  extraEnv: []\n\n# Volcano Agent Scheduler (optional)\nvolcano:\n  scheduler:\n    enabled: false\n    replicas: 1\n    image:\n      repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n      pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n      tag: \"latest\"\n```\n\n### 3. Workload Manager Template\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.replicas }}\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: workloadmanager\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: workloadmanager\n    spec:\n      {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n      imagePullSecrets:\n        {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n      {{- end }}\n      serviceAccountName: workloadmanager\n      containers:\n        - name: workloadmanager\n          image: \"{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.tag }}\"\n          imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy }}\n          ports:\n            - name: http\n              containerPort: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n              protocol: TCP\n          env:\n            - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n              valueFrom:\n                fieldRef:\n                  fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n            - name: REDIS_ADDR\n              value: {{ .Values.redis.addr | quote }}\n            - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n              valueFrom:\n                secretKeyRef:\n                  name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n                  key: password\n                  optional: true\n            {{- with .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}\n            {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n            {{- end }}\n          args:\n            - --port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n            - --runtime-class-name=\n          resources:\n            {{- toYaml .Values.workloadmanager.resources | nindent 12 }}\n          livenessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health\n              port: http\n            initialDelaySeconds: 10\n            periodSeconds: 10\n          readinessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health\n              port: http\n            initialDelaySeconds: 5\n            periodSeconds: 5\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  type: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.type }}\n  ports:\n    - port: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n      targetPort: http\n      protocol: TCP\n      name: http\n  selector:\n    app: workloadmanager\n```\n\n### 4. Router Template\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.router.replicas }}\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: agentcube-router\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: agentcube-router\n    spec:\n      {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n      imagePullSecrets:\n        {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n      {{- end }}\n      {{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n      serviceAccountName: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n      {{- end }}\n      containers:\n        - name: agentcube-router\n          image: \"{{ .Values.router.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.router.image.tag }}\"\n          imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.router.image.pullPolicy }}\n          ports:\n            - name: http\n              containerPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n              protocol: TCP\n          env:\n            - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n              valueFrom:\n                fieldRef:\n                  fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n            - name: REDIS_ADDR\n              value: {{ .Values.redis.addr | quote }}\n            - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n              valueFrom:\n                secretKeyRef:\n                  name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n                  key: password\n                  optional: true\n            - name: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n              value: \"http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\"\n            {{- with .Values.router.extraEnv }}\n            {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n            {{- end }}\n          args:\n            - --port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n            - --debug\n          resources:\n            {{- toYaml .Values.router.resources | nindent 12 }}\n          livenessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health/live\n              port: http\n            initialDelaySeconds: 1\n            periodSeconds: 2\n          readinessProbe:\n            httpGet:\n              path: /health/ready\n              port: http\n            initialDelaySeconds: 1\n            periodSeconds: 2\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  type: {{ .Values.router.service.type }}\n  ports:\n    - port: {{ .Values.router.service.port }}\n      targetPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n      protocol: TCP\n      name: http\n  selector:\n    app: agentcube-router\n```\n\n### 5. Workload Manager RBAC\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxclaims\", \"sandboxtemplates\", \"sandboxwarmpools\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxwarmpools/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]\n    verbs: [\"update\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"authentication.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"tokenreviews\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"secrets\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: workloadmanager\n    namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\nroleRef:\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: workloadmanager\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n```\n\n### 6. Router RBAC (Optional)\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml\n{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Role\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"secrets\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: RoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n    namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\nroleRef:\n  kind: Role\n  name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### 7. Volcano Agent Scheduler (Optional)\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ConfigMap\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\ndata:\n  agent-scheduler.conf: |\n    actions: \"allocate\"\n    tiers:\n      - plugins: \"predicates,nodeorder\"\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"apiextensions.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"customresourcedefinitions\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\", \"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"events\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"update\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods/binding\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"persistentvolumeclaims\", \"persistentvolumes\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"update\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"namespaces\", \"services\", \"replicationcontrollers\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"resourcequotas\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"nodes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"storage.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"storageclasses\", \"csinodes\", \"csidrivers\", \"csistoragecapacities\", \"volumeattachments\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"policy\"]\n    resources: [\"poddisruptionbudgets\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"scheduling.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"priorityclasses\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"scheduling.incubator.k8s.io\", \"scheduling.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"podgroups\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"update\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"configmaps\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"delete\", \"update\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"apps\"]\n    resources: [\"daemonsets\", \"replicasets\", \"statefulsets\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"coordination.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"leases\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"create\", \"update\", \"watch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"resource.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"resourceclaims\", \"resourceclaims/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"resource.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"deviceclasses\", \"resourceslices\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"shard.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"nodeshards\"]\n    verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\", \"update\"]\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler-role\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\nroleRef:\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler-service\n  annotations:\n    prometheus.io/scrape: \"true\"\n    prometheus.io/port: \"8080\"\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  ports:\n    - port: 8080\n      targetPort: 8080\n      name: metrics\n  selector:\n    app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n---\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\nspec:\n  replicas: {{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.replicas }}\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: volcano-agent-scheduler\n      containers:\n        - name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n          image: \"{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.tag }}\"\n          imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.pullPolicy }}\n          args:\n            - --scheduler-name=agent-scheduler\n            - --config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf\n          ports:\n            - containerPort: 8080\n              name: metrics\n          resources:\n            limits:\n              cpu: 500m\n              memory: 512Mi\n            requests:\n              cpu: 100m\n              memory: 128Mi\n          volumeMounts:\n            - name: config\n              mountPath: /config\n            - name: empty\n              mountPath: /tmp\n          securityContext:\n            runAsNonRoot: true\n            runAsUser: 1000\n      volumes:\n        - name: config\n          configMap:\n            name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n        - name: empty\n          emptyDir: {}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### 8. Redis Secret Template\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/templates/redis-secret.yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Secret\nmetadata:\n  name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n  namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: redis\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\ntype: Opaque\nstringData:\n  password: {{ .Values.redis.password | quote }}\n```\n\n### 9. .helmignore\n\n```\n# .helmignore\n# Patterns to ignore when building packages.\n.DS_Store\n.git/\n.gitignore\n.bzr/\n.bzrignore\n.hg/\n.hgignore\n.svn/\n*.swp\n*.bak\n*.tmp\n*.orig\n*~\n.project\n.idea/\n*.tmproj\n.vscode/\ntests/\n*.md\n!README.md\n```\n\n### 10. 更新 CodeInterpreter CRD\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml\n# 基于 deployment/design.md 中的 codeinterpreters CRD 定义\n# 包含完整的 OpenAPI v3 schema\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### 依赖影响\n\n| 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Helm | ≥3.0 | Chart 打包和部署 |\n| Kubernetes | ≥1.21 | API 兼容性 |\n| Redis | 任意 | 外部依赖（通过 values 配置） |\n\n### 模块依赖关系\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml                          # Chart 元数据\n├── values.yaml                         # 默认配置\n├── .helmignore                         # 打包忽略\n├── crds/\n│   ├── agentruntime.yaml               # AgentRuntime CRD (已存在)\n│   └── codeinterpreter.yaml            # CodeInterpreter CRD (新增)\n└── templates/\n    ├── _helpers.tpl                    # 模板辅助函数\n    ├── redis-secret.yaml               # Redis Secret\n    ├── workloadmanager.yaml            # Workload Manager Deployment + Service\n    ├── agentcube-router.yaml           # Router Deployment + Service\n    ├── rbac/\n    │   └── workloadmanager.yaml        # Workload Manager RBAC\n    ├── rbac-router.yaml                # Router RBAC (可选)\n    └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # Volcano Scheduler (可选)\n```\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n- 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n- values.yaml 默认值遵循 spec 定义，确保向后兼容\n- 可选组件默认禁用（router.rbac.create=false, volcano.scheduler.enabled=false）\n\n### 测试影响\n\n- 需要验证模板渲染的正确性（helm template）\n- 需要验证 values 覆盖行为\n- 需要验证可选组件的条件渲染\n- 需要验证 RBAC 权限的完整性\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 方案 1: 使用 Kustomize 替代 Helm\n\n**优点:**\n- 更轻量，无需额外工具\n- 原生支持 Kubernetes 声明式配置\n- 与 kubectl 集成更好\n\n**缺点:**\n- 缺少 values 配置树，参数化能力较弱\n- 不支持条件渲染（可选组件）\n- 缺少 release 管理和升级回滚机制\n\n**决策:** 选择 Helm，因为需要完整的配置管理和可选组件支持。\n\n### 方案 2: 单一巨型模板文件\n\n**优点:**\n- 文件数量少，结构简单\n- 易于复制粘贴\n\n**缺点:**\n- 难以维护和调试\n- 无法模块化组织\n- 不利于团队协作\n\n**决策:** 采用模块化模板组织（每个组件独立文件），提高可维护性。\n\n### 方案 3: 多 Chart 拆分（每个组件一个 Chart）\n\n**优点:**\n- 更细粒度的版本控制\n- 可以独立部署组件\n\n**缺点:**\n- 增加部署复杂度\n- 需要管理多个 Chart 版本\n- 不利于整体升级\n\n**决策:** 采用单一 Chart，因为组件间存在强耦合（如 Router 依赖 Workload Manager URL）。\n\n### 方案 4: 使用子 Chart 管理可选组件\n\n**优点:**\n- 可选组件完全隔离\n- 可以独立版本\n\n**缺点:**\n- 增加 Chart 复杂度\n- 需要额外的依赖管理\n\n**决策:** 采用条件渲染（`{{- if .Values.xxx }}`），保持单一 Chart 结构。\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 单元测试\n\n1. **values.yaml 验证** - 使用 yamllint 验证 YAML 语法\n2. **模板渲染测试** - `helm template` 验证生成的 YAML\n3. **条件渲染测试** - 验证可选组件在不同 values 下的行为\n4. **RBAC 验证** - 使用 `kubectl auth can-i` 验证权限\n\n### 集成测试\n\n1. **Kind 集群测试** - 在 Kind 集群上实际安装验证\n2. **升级测试** - 验证 `helm upgrade` 行为\n3. **回滚测试** - 验证 `helm rollback` 行为\n\n### 测试覆盖目标\n\n- Chart.yaml: 100%（所有字段正确）\n- values.yaml: 100%（所有配置项有效）\n- 模板文件: 100%（所有组件渲染正确）\n- 条件分支: 100%（可选组件启用/禁用均正确）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Chart.yaml 包含所有必需字段\n- [ ] values.yaml 包含完整的配置树\n- [ ] Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 正确渲染\n- [ ] Router Deployment 和 Service 正确渲染\n- [ ] Workload Manager RBAC 权限完整\n- [ ] Router RBAC 条件渲染正确\n- [ ] Volcano Scheduler 条件渲染正确\n- [ ] Redis Secret 正确注入\n- [ ] CRD 文件完整（agentruntimes + codeinterpreters）\n- [ ] `helm lint` 无警告\n- [ ] `helm template` 生成有效 YAML\n- [ ] `helm install` 在 Kind 集群上成功\n- [ ] 组件健康检查通过\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### 必需依赖\n- Helm ≥3.0\n- Kubernetes ≥1.21\n- Redis（外部部署）\n\n### 可选依赖\n- Volcano（仅当 volcano.scheduler.enabled=true）\n\n### 被依赖\n- AR-017 (CRD 定义)\n- AR-029 (SDK 部署配置)\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n### 从手动部署迁移\n\n1. 备份现有资源配置\n2. 更新 values.yaml 匹配当前配置\n3. 运行 `helm install` 安装新 Chart\n4. 验证组件运行正常\n5. 删除旧资源\n\n### 破坏性变更\n无 - 首次实现。\n\n### 行为变更\n- Redis 配置从环境变量改为通过 Secret 注入\n- RBAC 资源名称标准化为组件名\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. 是否支持多集群部署？（未来通过 values 覆盖实现）\n2. 是否需要支持外部 Redis Operator？（待需求明确）\n3. 是否需要集成监控和日志配置？（作为未来增强）\n\n## References\n\n- `deployment/spec.md` - 部署规范\n- `deployment/design.md` - 部署设计\n- `manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml` - 现有 CRD\n- Helm Best Practices: https://helm.sh/docs/chart_best_practices/\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml\">\nERROR [126:48] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\nERROR [138:48] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/ds